{"lastModified":1749149720448,"uri":"c::7819198761::vessel::d5cca3e7-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Italy\n\nFilippetti Flybridge 76 JOY is the essence of charm and comfort. The heartbeat of the Filippetti Flybridge 76 is elegance. A revolutionary concept has been designed to satisfy the most refined and demanding owners. In this context, space becomes an essential element of naval architecture: it presents a living area on the main deck with dimensions never seen before and invents the external bow resignation. The exterior of the Flybridge 76 stands out, fine and elegant is a glance on the horizon: it has a dinette and external cushions covered with fabrics of great value. The interiors, spacious and comfortable, offer a relaxing navigation. Below deck, the Filippetti Flybridge 76 JOY has 4 cabins, all equipped with every comfort: en suite services, LCD TV and a spacious wardrobe. Those looking for peace and tranquility can rest comfortably in the flybridge: climbing two comfortable stairs can access the upper deck and enjoy the thrill of navigation, the sea breeze and the relaxation offered by the large areas available.","blueprint":{"name":"JOY","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3e7-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c5c61750-3d5a-11f0-b9b6-3b22d9e5c726/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3e7-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::d18daf80-3d5a-11f0-b9b7-3b22d9e5c726/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3e7-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::d17879d0-3d5a-11f0-b9b6-3b22d9e5c726/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3e7-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::d177b680-3d5a-11f0-b9b6-3b22d9e5c726/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3e7-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::d18af060-3d5a-11f0-b9b6-3b22d9e5c726/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cca3e7-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::d179d960-3d5a-11f0-b9b6-3b22d9e5